select `sec`.*, `ab`.`branch_name` from `academic_section` as `sec` left join `academic_branch` as `ab` on `ab`.`id_branch` = `sec`.`branch_id` where `sec`.`status_id` = 1

select count(*) as aggregate from `student_info` as `student` left join `student_class_assignment` as `sca` on `student`.`id_student` = `sca`.`student_id` left join `academic_branch` as `ab` on `ab`.`id_branch` = `sca`.`branch_id` left join `academic_class` as `ac` on `ac`.`id_class` = `sca`.`class_id` left join `academic_section` as `section` on `section`.`id_section` = `sca`.`section_id` left join `academic_shift` as `shift` on `shift`.`id_shift` = `sca`.`shift_id` where `ac`.`status_id` = 1
